n again at any time by unchecking \"Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information\" and clicking the \"Save My Preferences\" button.</p>\";s:9:\"optOption\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:44:\"Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information\";s:6:\"enable\";s:6:\"Enable\";s:7:\"disable\";s:7:\"Disable\";}}s:9:\"gpcOption\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:1:{s:11:\"description\";s:188:\"<p>Your opt-out settings for this website have been respected since we detected a <b>Global Privacy Control</b> signal from your browser and, therefore, you cannot change this setting.</p>\";}}s:8:\"showLess\";s:9:\"Show less\";s:8:\"showMore\";s:9:\"Show more\";s:7:\"buttons\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:2:{s:6:\"cancel\";s:6:\"Cancel\";s:7:\"confirm\";s:19:\"Save My Preferences\";}}s:13:\"optoutSuccess\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:2:{s:4:\"text\";s:41:\"Your opt-out preference has been honored.\";s:7:\"subtext\";s:72:\"Banner closes automatically in <span id=\"ckyCountdownTimer\"></span> s...\";}}s:11:\"closeButton\";s:5:\"Close\";}}s:14:\"revisitConsent\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Consent Preferences\";}}s:10:\"auditTable\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:2:{s:7:\"headers\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:3:{s:2:\"id\";s:6:\"Cookie\";s:8:\"duration\";s:8:\"Duration\";s:11:\"description\";s:11:\"Description\";}}s:7:\"message\";s:22:\"No cookies to display.\";}}s:16:\"videoPlaceholder\";a:1:{s:8:\"elements\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";s:44:\"Please accept cookies to access this content\";}}}}s:14:\"banner_default\";i:0;s:6:\"status\";i:0;}}','on');
