e, mailing address, telephone number, and email address. A statement consenting to the jurisdiction of the Federal District Court for the judicial district in which your address is located (or, if outside the United States, any judicial district in which MiniWebGames.com may be found), and that you will accept service of process from the person who filed the original DMCA notice. Upon receipt of a valid counter-notice, MiniWebGames.com will forward it to the original complainant. If the complainant does not initiate a court action within ten (10) business days, the removed content may be restored at our discretion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":6} -->\n<ol start=\"6\" class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Repeat Infringer Policy In accordance with DMCA § 512(i)(1)(A), MiniWebGames.com maintains a policy of terminating, in appropriate circumstances, the accounts of users who are determined to be repeat infringers. A user who receives three (3) or more substantiated copyright infringement notices may have their account suspended or permanently terminated at the sole discretion of MiniWebGames.com. We reserve the right to act sooner in cases of serious or willful infringement.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Disclaimer This DMCA Policy does not constitute legal advice. MiniWebGames.com recommends consulting a qualified attorney before submitting a takedown notice or counter-notice. The rights and remedies available under the DMCA are in addition to any other rights and remedies available under applicable law.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Contact For questions or concerns regarding this policy, please contact:</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Email: thanhlong.bkpro@gmail.com Website: https://miniwebgames.com</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','DMCA','','inherit','closed','closed','','82-revision-v1','','','2026-06-30 