e Safari or Chrome browser and play on the go.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How do I save my game progress or find my favorite games?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Simply create a free account and tap the heart icon on any game page. This saves the game directly to your personal favorites dashboard for instant access during your next visit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:template-part {\"slug\":\"footer\",\"theme\":\"webgames\"} /--></main>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Front Page','Displays your site\'s homepage, whether it is set to display latest posts or a static page. The Front Page template takes precedence over all templates.','inherit','closed','closed','','97-revision-v1','','','2026-07-02 02:48:03','2026-07-02 02:48:03','',97,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=119',0,'revision','',0);
