nk-color has-small-font-size\" style=\"color:#bed1e3\">Simply create a free account and tap the heart icon on any game page. This saves the game directly to your personal favorites dashboard for instant access during your next visit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:template-part {\"slug\":\"footer\",\"theme\":\"webgames\"} /--></main>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Front Page','Displays your site\'s homepage, whether it is set to display latest posts or a static page. The Front Page template takes precedence over all templates.','inherit','closed','closed','','97-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 04:09:07','2026-07-03 04:09:07','',97,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=217',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (218,1,'2026-07-05 01:49:44','2026-07-05 01:49:44','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sprunki Sonic: Create Music with Sonic and Friends</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduction</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Sonic</strong> transforms familiar Sonic-inspired characters into a colorful rhythm playground where creativity takes center stage. Instead of racing through levels or battling enemies, you\'ll experiment with sounds, combine unique performers, and build your own musical compositions. Every arrangement creates a different mix, making each session feel fresh and rewarding for players who enjoy music creation and casual browser games.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":219,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://miniwebgames.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/sprunki-sonic-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-219\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About the Game</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Sonic is a browser-based <strong>music creation game</strong> inspired by the Sprunki style of interactive sound mixing. The game replaces traditional platforming action with a simple drag-and-drop music system featuring Sonic-themed characters.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Your objective is to build original musical performances by placing different performers onto the stage. Each character contributes a unique beat, melody, vocal effect, or rhythm. Mixing multiple characters together creates layered songs that can range from relaxing tunes to energetic soundtracks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">There are no enemies, timers, or difficult missions. Instead, success comes from experimenting with different combinations and discovering new musical arrangements that match your personal style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to Play</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Playing Sprunki Sonic is easy, even for first-time players.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use your mouse to drag available characters onto the stage.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Each performer instantly begins adding a unique musical sound.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Continue combining different characters to build a complete composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Remove or replace performers at any time to change your mix.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Keep experimenting until you create a soundtrack you enjoy.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The main goal is to produce creative music by discovering combinations that sound great together rather than reaching a traditional ending.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sonic-inspired characters redesigned for a musical adventure.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Simple drag-and-drop controls suitable for every skill level.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Multiple character combinations that create unique sound mixes.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Bright, colorful animations that react to your music.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Relaxing gameplay focused on creativity instead of competition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Start with a rhythm character before adding melodies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Introduce one performer at a time to hear each sound clearly.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Swap characters frequently to discover hidden musical combinations.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Balance beats, vocals, and effects for a fuller composition.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\">Replay your favorite mixes and experiment with small adjustments.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Similar Games</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Infected</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Sprunki Incredibox</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<li class=\"has-small-font-size\"><strong>Friday Night Funkin\'</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Sprunki Sonic offers a refreshing take on music creation by combining recognizable Sonic-inspired characters with simple interactive gameplay. Its accessible controls, endless sound combinations, and creative freedom make it an enjoyable choice for anyone who loves casual rhythm games and experimenting with original musical performances.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sprunki Sonic','','publish','open','closed','','sprunki-sonic','','','2026-07-05 10:04:27','2026-07-05 10:04:27','',0,'https://miniwebgames.local/?post_type=game&#038;p=218',0,'game','',0);
