te:</strong> July 8, 2026</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 8, 2026</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Terms Of Service','','inherit','closed','closed','','78-revision-v1','','','2026-07-08 05:14:22','2026-07-08 05:14:22','',78,'https://miniwebgames.local/?p=256',0,'revision','',0);
